::Fenox::

Fenox heard D growl near her, giving him another pat. She briefly 
wondered why he was reacting like this. Perhaps he knew something she 
didn't? Maybe Vlad was a threat? But she doubted that. A bot would 
have to be suicidal to do anything threatening in an enemy base, 
especially one like the Iron Fist.

She looked back at Vlad, waiting for him to speak.
